{"lastModified":1761078452307,"uri":"c::35186983531::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nExperience the Thrill of Luxury: TECNOMAR MADRAS 64 - BOND 007 Set sail on the TECNOMAR MADRAS 64 - BOND 007, a high-speed marvel that redefines luxury at sea. Accommodating up to 12 guests this vessel is your passport to unparalleled opulence.\n\nEquipped with every conceivable comfort, this motor yacht boasts both front and back sundecks for soaking up the sun, a lounge-filled deck area, and a swim platform with a convenient sea ladder. Inside, you'll find a master cabin with a private bathroom, two guest cabins with en-suite bathrooms, a well-appointed kitchen, and a stylish salon and bar area.\n\nEntertainment at Your Fingertips: Stay cool and connected with full air conditioning, and keep your favorite refreshments at the perfect temperature with the onboard refrigerator and freezer. Entertainment options abound, from Bluetooth/USB/iPhone player, and flat-screen smart TV, to the complimentary WiFi that keeps you in touch while you explore.\nSeize the Moment: Don’t just dream about it—make it happen! Cruise through the sparkling Adriatic, bask in the luxury, and create memories you’ll treasure forever. This is more than a boat—it’s your ticket to the good life.","blueprint":{"name":"TECNOMAR MADRAS 64","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414::assets::f00eb6c0-51d7-11f0-b390-8922bee4ee86/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414::assets::b6e59060-51d4-11f0-af36-8fb85498f209/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414::assets::b6e2f850-51d4-11f0-af36-8fb85498f209/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414::assets::b6d67530-51d4-11f0-af36-8fb85498f209/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2d62dd0-51ce-11f0-9a62-7b6d93a55414::as